Gemfile.lock

# Fastlane run artifacts
fastlane/report.xml
fastlane/test_output
fastlane/Preview.html

# Generated Xcode project (xcodegen is the source of truth — run `xcodegen generate`)
**.xcodeproj
**.xcworkspace
**.xcscheme
**.pbxproj

**/Secrets.plist
**/.idea/
